item.title: You Have A Voice Use It with Baltimore Indie Rocker, Will Sims
item.description: Welcome to this week’s Indie Artist Music Hustle with Blonde Intelligence. This week’s guest is Will Sims, Baltimore rocker. He discusses his latest album to be released October 9, 2023, You Have A Voice Use It.  He has a single released now from the album, To Remind You.
